  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-66d6b3db-b200-42bb-a364-63538407bb4f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63c53964-fc7b-4c80-8e4c-e0897c471446\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-489806da-23a6-4e75-b92d-5c3d36c37ba0\">4월 말에 만들었던 공진단을 환자분들이 많이 사랑해주셔서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f8ffc926-6465-421c-aac4-26598e7586e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae6e5064-aaa9-4cb8-8eb8-8162ff745cf5\">재고가 바닥 났네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-36c685ea-e88f-4ddf-89bc-19b380a08d36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ea530cc-8e82-46f7-9cec-5e5e086fe7a8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1db89714-b0f4-4fc0-9cc4-9abf8fdd3ac8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-512f5196-eb03-4861-9961-e3e2df1e781d\">그래서 공진단을 다시 만들기 위해 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-35ce8d98-83a7-4d59-8252-a53508b55dbd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-744309b2-bb19-41ae-816c-21eb2ba007a1\">공진단 만들 재료들을 검수했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-326d7ec6-02d0-4c39-a6fd-d5c9b26be8b3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-21e9f780-f43f-4ebd-b3f7-dcef6a0d2d66\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-66d6b3db-b200-42bb-a364-63538407bb4f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-imageStrip se-imageStrip2 se-l-default\" id=\"SE-94ec3f6a-9f8e-4556-bdc6-28c8a31be08e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-imageStrip se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-imageStrip-container se-imageStrip-col-2\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ed0913d2-bb41-4149-893f-e90c2e667686\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b19d3fc77e98fe16.jpg", \"originalWidth\" : \"960\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1280\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b19d3fc77e98fe16.jpg" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b19d3fc77e98fe16.jpg" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"666\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bd2675d0-885d-4cea-9507-47cd171c85dc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fb0af644d144cf43.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"960\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1280\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fb0af644d144cf43.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fb0af644d144cf43.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"666\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_imageStrip\", \"id\": \"SE-94ec3f6a-9f8e-4556-bdc6-28c8a31be08e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"imageStrip\", \"images\": [ {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"id\": \"SE-ed0913d2-bb41-4149-893f-e90c2e667686\", \"ai\": \"false\" } , {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"id\": \"SE-bd2675d0-885d-4cea-9507-47cd171c85dc\", \"ai\": \"false\" } ] }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6174d591-15f3-41b4-bea2-9861835d1157\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ae80ec9-8f24-46c9-9837-abde3a4f5e0c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29d8d8b2-4c95-4e68-8dbf-b5de0c9ff1a5\">당귀와 산수류는 경희한약의 당귀, 산수유를 선택했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7832d655-5fea-46e7-bb84-638ee5ea1c32\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c8a9059-041c-4789-8172-67c76f8d7a30\">경희한약은 경희대학교 부설 경희의료원 한방병원에 한약재를 전속 공급하는 곳이라 품질이 좋습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9fe91342-b515-4f73-9f3c-4d279d76674e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6d50548-71fe-49f8-b4bd-815c8107fbb8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2519dec0-932c-4703-b832-16b9af817b9c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5dffa0d4-ed63-453f-8fff-96ff8c941f2d\">약재의 색도 좋고 향과 질감도 만족스럽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e1e6b8ec-5b6b-45f4-b013-0ad08e3bad73\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6cecd429-bbb4-44f3-be4f-13e67c33b2b9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6174d591-15f3-41b4-bea2-9861835d1157\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f7a31f8a-acf9-4c13-b3ea-3a521ec8e6a5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f7a31f8a-acf9-4c13-b3ea-3a521ec8e6a5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9af39f8e92b59eb0.jpg", \"originalWidth\" : \"1204\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1280\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9af39f8e92b59eb0.jpg" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9af39f8e92b59eb0.jpg" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"531\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-f7a31f8a-acf9-4c13-b3ea-3a521ec8e6a5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02e04b12-52b8-4003-8f9e-11b36b32397b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bebfcdbf-1565-4356-a112-f0013c8fb5d5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-af821de3-11d7-407e-8c1c-ae01e8de0f96\">녹용은 실물을 보러 직접 다녀왔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7eebdf50-d9d8-43dc-a4d8-9fd2462d6c4c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9bb2a703-093b-4a1c-8018-b0816e36fb3d\">제가 손에 들고 있는 것이 녹용 한 덩어리입니다.  녹용 &#x27;전지&#x27;라고 부르죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-503a2812-1a3a-4ee7-a08c-dcb35d1c2ee4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cad6b06a-75c3-4957-bdf7-516ce749adc6\">녹용의 아래쪽은 단단하고 유효성분이 적습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b230366d-fafc-42ba-8993-05a2daabd6b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5de6c4fa-e99d-427f-901a-b55078313666\">그래서 녹용의 자라는 성장부위인 상단 끝 부위 위주로 사용하게 됩니다. 성장부가 튼실하고 모양이 좋은 것을 골라야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-91d6e522-25c4-4a59-97fc-c06da374e263\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2aa308cc-c870-4cf9-aac8-9615e5cb88d2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-02ee5e82-2b4e-434a-bc2a-b48f83be0486\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7881facc-daa1-4fd3-8978-203180683a83\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-02e04b12-52b8-4003-8f9e-11b36b32397b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-collage\" id=\"SE-a4f583c5-f268-4a9d-8c35-fbb08208543d\">\n                            <div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n                                <div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n                                    \n                                    <div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:53.174265019173404%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-0bbce81d-9c1b-45a0-a4fd-d40481476969\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0bbce81d-9c1b-45a0-a4fd-d40481476969\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10fde93055096202.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2669\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3133\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10fde93055096202.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10fde93055096202.jpg\" data-width=\"936\" data-height=\"1099\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:46.825734980826596%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-4bc1342e-bdca-4a01-9f2b-67b4cf9c7be8\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4bc1342e-bdca-4a01-9f2b-67b4cf9c7be8\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d5a78d3ab7c6250b.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4032\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d5a78d3ab7c6250b.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d5a78d3ab7c6250b.jpg\" data-width=\"936\" data-height=\"1248\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_imageGroup\", \"id\" :\"SE-a4f583c5-f268-4a9d-8c35-fbb08208543d\", \"data\": { \"layout\" : \"collage\" }}' data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_imageGroup\", \"id\": \"SE-a4f583c5-f268-4a9d-8c35-fbb08208543d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"imageGroup\", \"layout\": \"collage\", \"images\": [ {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"id\": \"SE-0bbce81d-9c1b-45a0-a4fd-d40481476969\", \"ai\": \"false\" } , {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"id\": \"SE-4bc1342e-bdca-4a01-9f2b-67b4cf9c7be8\", \"ai\": \"false\" } ] }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b323f98-c6bb-4edd-968a-80a2d99fb76a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3878be9-703c-4796-8368-090d9fb203f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a60a796-2764-486c-a25e-9cc2f61d1dc8\">사향은 CITE 라 해서 멸종위기 동물로 관리됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-208acc7b-2142-4585-9b45-097d6c44ff36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6c316e9-edf6-4dd2-90ac-a28d265969a5\">그래서 정식 수입되는 것만 사용해야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-470cf4bb-d875-4e1a-85ec-cf82df6a7617\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9f5fa05d-5b08-4665-bede-a265ea3169f7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb59d58e-821e-4c72-8314-52a42a8eae90\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a501fb5-ef2a-4218-a473-999c2e851059\">또한 고가의 약재이기 때문에 가짜가 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a543af1c-a4d4-43f7-b94f-7cf78366774b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f1523ba4-d675-4141-ba99-d9f50e3b8d13\">그래서 위의 사진에서 보듯이 식품의약품안전처에서 붙여놓은 &#x27;정품인증 스티커&#x27;가 있는 사향을 써야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-32ea33bb-2dce-4fe8-ac60-258b9ea46692\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27c982de-71ae-458e-85c3-15ce0ca41bd2\">원래 향과 질감을 보고 더 우수한 것을 고르기도 하는데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0174f3be-a78b-48c0-9e32-79146d525aed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-36977214-b513-42ce-b012-e037a80284a5\">위 사진처럼 밀봉되어 있기 때문에 병 속의 성상을 육안으로 보고 고를 뿐, 향을 맡아볼 수는 없어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63fb6642-6c3e-4078-9eb8-6b3a1c208109\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-707e3cba-fd56-49e8-b471-e25411c8e6e0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-10f64f13-acee-474e-95ef-b3f3c11164ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85053832-e5bb-4b99-a3be-90bcbd1b5f05\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ad8b001-e4b3-4094-aaec-263a2e98b14b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2a3f29f0-0e45-439d-884a-561ce81b1fe0\">이 약재들을 세척 가공하고, ,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-36c66ec1-c5fa-40a1-b9b9-4f055a1ee71f\"><span 