t\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d74a1c8-a99c-45e3-93e4-3a60a7daa388\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a326c46c-00a4-4d9f-b12c-cd9a23d68a9f\">다 만들어지면 이런 모양이 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f482d7bd-42c3-4dac-b77b-13b78ec39bd5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1700c6ab-fc5f-4d64-b7b8-9f6e550c46c5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24beea04-40c1-4556-b87a-43d6127ffea3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9b44b357-0934-4793-8e4a-9f1b95f7283b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b979d6f6-8f2f-480a-9691-58f2ce9810f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28d99370-878b-4792-be7c-6b74d34e88c1\">공진단은 사향이 들어있는 오리지널 &quot;원방&quot;공진단과</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ce73b4d-55c8-4ec1-acbd-1edc584bb47b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-52ec99aa-2c14-4836-8330-7671e5342636\">사향이 너무 비싸니 증상이 심하지 않은 환자분들이 복용할 수 있게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e03ae9ae-d225-4c7e-939d-66572a43606d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e6dc0b8d-420d-47d7-8a74-76a1af4a1f3b\">사향을 뺀 &#x27;녹용&#x27;공진단 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c51a8ba4-dc94-4923-8e59-c740e8446d44\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b061a52c-ca00-4e7a-a2c6-72733d59de52\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-07cdfeb9-634e-4753-adbe-f45b7b3c0c71\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c360a088-e5cc-437f-a69a-fdc294f3d6c7\">두 가지로 만들게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-86d6a1b7-890b-4da9-98f1-7906f4e6bd52\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0de2adea-de85-4fcb-80f1-5593a9b38b14\">증상이 심하고 기력을 많이 보해야 하는 환자는 가격이 비싸지만  원방공진단을 처방하고,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-840dff8f-8150-4d20-bddd-f9ecca059b52\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-41b287e3-97b6-414e-b74d-ad71debb68ce\">증상이 아직 완고하게 심하진 않은 환자분들 또는 병세가 회복되어가는 환자분들은 녹용공진단을 처방하게 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2aa423cf-e529-4f00-b20e-eb876c3a8864\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-40fbabaf-00a6-4fef-a688-2d30822db57a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9311155b-fb69-4d59-b99f-ca98af76fefa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-730ac0fc-80d2-477f-8eb4-59511f25d760\">잘 만들겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77913a31-e212-4803-bd5e-ae88c2b870e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2cccdcd-d1ec-4156-aed8-8e657c17f74b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-14b0cffb-d566-402f-b5a7-de434d8f8065\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b05f374a-4a1e-46b0-8401-3e236d2cb311\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\"